how to run docker and freqtrade


INRO:  This repo is set up to run freqtrade using the docker seamlessly using the command line command "freqtrade". 
       To enable this ability source the utils/sourcme file.  It defines a function called "freqtrade" which executes the docker command for freqtrade. 
	
to build a docker image run this:

docker-compose build --pull
